---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="yyyyang | Docs" description="yyyyang 的文档入口。">
  <Fragment slot="hero">
    <div class="hero-grid">
      <div class="hero-copy">
        <p class="eyebrow">Docs / Structure</p>
        <h1>文档继续归档，但不再直接裸露成仓库文件列表。</h1>
        <p class="lead">这里作为文档总入口，后续所有说明、规划和资料继续按目录整理。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Fragment>

  <section class="panel">
    <div class="contact-links">
      <a class="contact-link" href="/docs/about/personal-profile/">
        <strong>About</strong>
        <span>个人介绍与对外资料</span>
      </a>
      <a class="contact-link" href="/docs/guides/custom-domain-and-https/">
        <strong>Guides</strong>
        <span>配置与操作说明</span>
      </a>
      <a class="contact-link" href="/docs/plans/site-roadmap/">
        <strong>Plans</strong>
        <span>站点规划与路线</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
